posts.title: RS/ SG/ W Einbrüche im Bergischen Städtedreieck
posts.text:
Wuppertal - 
Seit gestern (06.11.2017) nahm die Polizei im Bergischen Städtedreieck mehrere Einbrüche und Einbruchsversuche auf: 
Remscheid. In der Nacht zu gestern stiegen Unbekannte in zwei Gaststätten an der Bismarckstraße ein. Sie brachen die Spielautomaten auf und entwendeten Bargeld, bevor sie unerkannt entkamen. Im Zeitraum vom 01.11.2017 bis gestern hebelten Einbrecher die Terrassentür eines Hauses an der Mixsieper Straße auf. Sie entwendeten Schmuck und flüchteten unerkannt. Am vergangenen Wochenende versuchten Unbekannte eine Balkontür einer Wohnung an der Sedanstraße aufzuhebeln. Sie scheiterten jedoch an der guten Sicherung und entkamen unverrichteter Dinge. 
Solingen. Eine Gaststätte an der Hasselstraße war in der Nacht zu Montag das Ziel von Einbrechern. Sie durchsuchten den Schankraum, brachen Spielautomaten auf und entwendeten Bargeld bevor sie unerkannt flüchteten. In eine Wohnung an der Bozener Straße brachen Diebe gestern Nachmittag ein. Sie durchsuchten zwar die Räume, erbeuteten jedoch offenbar nichts. Ebenso scheiterten Einbrecher in der Drosselstraße. Sie hebelten ein Fenster einer Wohnung auf, gelangten hinein, machten aber keine Beute. 
Wuppertal. Auf ein Büro an der Paradestraße hatten es Einbrecher am vergangenen Wochenende abgesehen. Nachdem sie die Räume durchsucht hatten stahlen sie Bargeld und flüchteten unerkannt. Ebenfalls ein Büro war das Ziel von Dieben an der Laurentiusstraße. Sie brachen mehrere Räume auf und erbeuteten Laptops und Bargeld. Am Hofkamp stiegen bereits am Samstagabend Einbrecher über den Balkon in eine Wohnung ein. Während der Inhaber schlief nahmen sie einen Laptop, ein Handy und eine Tasche mit. An der Leibuschstraße drangen gestern Vormittag Täter in ein Einfamilienhaus ein und entwendeten Schmuck und eine Kamera. 
Hinweise zu den Einbrüchen nimmt die Polizei unter der Telefonnummer 0202/284-0 entgegen. Einen Termin für eine Beratung zum Thema Einbruchschutz erhalten Sie bei Ihrer Dienststelle "Kriminalprävention und Opferschutz" unter der Rufnummer 0202/284-1801. (cw)

posts.text:
Vui mừng chào đón thành viên thứ ba của đại gia đình Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn
 Nhà hàng Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn chính thức có mặt tại 75 Xuân Thuỷ, phường Thảo Điền, Quận 2 vào ngày 08/11/2017 trong sự háo hức của các tín đồ ẩm thực truyền thống Việt Nam.
Là một trong những nhà hàng món Việt nổi tiếng tại Sài Gòn, v ới hơn 20 năm truyền tải những dấu ấn Việt đặc sắc qua món cơm niêu, cơm đập và đa dạng món ăn truyền thống khác. Nhà hàng Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn tại 75 Xuân Thuỷ sẽ là một địa chỉ mà nhiều tín đồ sành ăn mong muốn tìm về. Sở hữu không gian ấm cúng mang hơi hướng Á Đông với nhiều điểm nhấn tinh tế kết hợp hòan hảo với yếu tố thiên nhiên, nhà hàng không chỉ phù hợp với doanh nhân, gia đình Việt mà còn được nhiều thực khách quốc tế lựa chọn khi muốn tìm hiểu về ẩm thực Việt Nam.
https://scontent.fsgn4-1.fna.fbcdn.n...28&oe=5AA2D2E8
Nếu đã từng trót mê màn trình diễn cơm đập tại Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn, bạn vẫn có thể được thưởng thức hương vị cơm đập giòn tan theo đúng nghĩa “đập” tại 75 Xuân Thuỷ mà không phải là nhà hàng nào khác. Nhà hàng chăm chút từ trong khâu chọn niêu, loại niêu đế mỏng được nung già trong nhiệt độ cao đảm bảo độ bền. Thức gạo nấu cũng là gạo Tám Xoan ngon dẻo, thơm phức, được chọn lựa kĩ càng từ vựa lúa lớn nhất cả nước. Cơm được nấu hoàn toàn thủ công trên bếp củi để đảm bảo đủ lửa và chín đều. Và khi cơm chín, thực khách sẽ được xem màn đập niêu lấy cơm ngay tại bàn điệu nghệ như những người nghệ sĩ tung hứng thực thụ.
Bên cạnh đó Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn còn sở hữu một thực đơn khá “hoành tráng” gồm hơn 200 món ăn đặc trưng của ba miền, với đầy đủ món khai vị, món chính, món đặc biệt, như: cơm cháy chả cá, bồ câu quay phong xa, canh cua khoai môn rau nhúc, gỏi sứa trộn vả, cua lột chiên giòn, tôm càng kho tàu, cá bống trứng kho tộ, canh chua cá hoặc tôm, canh cua đồng rau đay,… Với những hương, sắc và vị trên, như mang đến cho thực khách những hình ảnh quen thuộc của tuổi thơ có bà, có mẹ, đưa bạn trở về với mái nhà ấm êm, bên mâm cơm nóng sum vầy, đoàn tụ.
Thưởng thức những món ăn dân dã, bên trong gian nhà gỗ truyền thống chắc hẳn là một trải nghiệm vô cùng tuyệt vời mà bạn nhất định không thể bỏ qua. Hãy đến với Cơm Niêu Sài Gòn 75 Xuân Thuỷ để cùng khám phá nghệ thuật ẩm thực truyền thống Việt Nam.

posts.title: 像营养学家那样吃零食
posts.text: 新华社北京11月7日电（记者 黄敏） 很多人喜欢在两餐之间吃点零食补充能量。那怎样吃得美味营养又健康，英国《每日邮报》刊载了美国纽约两名注册营养师科琳·韦伯和加比·伯科的专业意见。 两人都认为两餐之间可以加点零食。韦伯说，健康零食有助增强营养，避免正餐时过度进食，减少对垃圾食品的渴望，保持人体能量水平。伯科建议午后3点左右吃零食，此时正是人体能量低谷，应该适当补充，以免过度饥饿，然后饥不择食。 至于选什么样的零食，两位营养学家认为，完美零食应当含有20克蛋白质，还有纤维素和健康脂肪，总热量低于200卡路里，添加的糖少于6克。蛋白质能强健肌肉，加速代谢；纤维素有助增加饱腹感；健康脂肪是指不饱和脂肪或者植物脂肪，比如橄榄油、坚果、牛油果等，有助延长饱腹感。 两人推荐的零食食谱包括：小杯希腊酸奶，加点水果，再加一把坚果；一个苹果或者香蕉，加一把花生或者黄油杏仁；半个花生黄油全麦三明治，加一杯低脂高蛋白奶酪；高纤维全麦饼干加几小块牛油果。 (原标题：像营养学家那样吃零食)

See the reaction of OAU VC on rumoured fee hike Published on November 7 2017 by Salam Rasak O. 
The Vice Chancellor of the Obafemi Awolowo University ( OAU ) Ile-Ife has denounced the rumour on the school fee hike. 
The Vice Chancellor, Prof Eyitope Ogunbodede said, "there is nothing like fee increment. The management has said nothing like that. People are just being mysterious and by this they spread false news around 
“I wonder how someone would just sit in his room and come up with a propaganda like that. People are just delighted in carrying fake news around and people get to believe that easily without getting the source or getting to know if it’s right or wrong” he said.. 
There is nothing like that, it’s just a lie. I don’t think there would be something like that in the session and the one that follows. It is not even in the plan of the university management” he added.

posts.text:
Jalani Laga Usiran Kontra Persib, Borneo FC Bawa 21 Pemain ant, Jurnalis · Selasa 07 November 2017, 16:44 WIB A A A 
SAMARINDA - Borneo FC membawa 21 pemain saat menjalani laga usiran tanpa penonton melawan Persib Bandung pada lanjutan kompetisi Liga 1 di Stadion Mulawarman Bontang, Kalimantan Timur, Rabu 8 November 2017. Pelatih Borneo FC Iwan Setiawan menjelaskan, pemain yang dibawa ke Bontang mayoritas pemain utama yang tidak diberangkatkan saat tandang ke markas Perseru Serui, Papua, pada akhir pekan lalu. 
Mereka di antaranya Lerby Eliandri, Sultan Samma, Terens Puhiri, Flavio Beck Junior, Yamashita Kunihiro, dan Matheus Lopes yang siap kembali memperkuat Borneo FC. Asisten pelatih Borneo FC Ahmad Amiruddin menambahkan bahwa timnya sudah bersiap menghadapi Persib Bandung dengan kekuatan terbaik dan menargetkan angka penuh. BERITA TERKAIT + Ditanya soal Pembentukan Skuad Musim Depan, Manajer Sriwijaya FC Ogah Ikut Campur 
"Kami sudah menyiapkan segalanya untuk melawan Persib Bandung. Tidak ada masalah cedera maupun akumulasi pemain utama. Hanya Shane Smeltz yang tidak ikut karena harus bermain untuk negaranya di playoff Piala Dunia 2018," ujar Amir. 
Humas Borneo FC Hedly Sundana mengatakan bahwa seluruh persiapan untuk menggelar pertandingan usiran sudah matang. Tim tamu Persib Bandung juga sudah tiba di Kota Bontang pada Senin malam. Persib dijadwalkan akan mencoba lapangan Stadion Mulawarman pada hari ini, Selasa (7/11/2017). 
"Semua sudah siap di Bontang. Ini laga usiran dan tanpa penonton. Persib menginap di hotel Oaktree Bontang, mereka dijadwalkan latihan jam 4 sore," kata Hedly. 
Laga hukuman tanpa penonton melawan Persib Bandung seharusnya digelar pada awal Oktober lalu, namun jadwal itu direvisi. Selain melawan Maung Bandung, tim Borneo FC juga telah menjalani laga usiran tanpa penonton melawan Persiba Balikpapan di Bontang. 
(Ram)

Bayaran Haji Kekal, Tidak Membebankan Rakyat Published on Nov 7, 2017 in Utama & Sensasi 
KUALA LUMPUR – Lembaga Tabung Haji (TH) perlu menanggung subsidi hampir RM400 juta, bagi musim haji tahun depan (1439H/2018M), dalam usaha mengekalkan bayaran RM9,980 kepada setiap jemaahnya. 
Subsidi itu meningkat berbanding RM300 juta bagi musim lalu, susulan peningkatan kos sebenar sebanyak 15 peratus, menyebabkan kos haji naik kepada RM22,450 seorang, berbanding RM19,550 pada musim lalu. 
Pengarah Urusan Kumpulan dan Ketua Pegawai Eksekutif TH, Datuk Seri Johan Abdullah, berkata pengekalan bayaran haji RM9,980 yang dilaksanakan sejak 2009 itu adalah inisiatif kerajaan yang prihatin terhadap kebajikan rakyat, khususnya umat Islam negara ini untuk menunaikan Rukun Islam kelima. 
Beliau berkata, subsidi haji hampir RM400 juta yang ditanggung adalah tanggungjawab sosial korporat terbesar TH, bagi mendukung aspirasi kerajaan mengimbangi keunggulan duniawi dan ukhrawi. 
“Ia selaras hasrat kerajaan supaya lebih ramai umat Islam negara ini dapat menunaikan ibadah haji dengan kos yang tidak membebankan. 
“Subsidi haji yang akan diberikan kepada seorang jemaah haji muassasah kali pertama ialah sebanyak RM12,470 iaitu 56 peratus daripada kos haji, manakala jemaah haji hanya perlu membayar RM9,980 iaitu 44 peratus daripada kos haji,” katanya dalam kenyataan hari ini. 
Dalam kenyataan sama, TH menjelaskan bayaran haji itu adalah kos yang paling rendah di Asia Tenggara dengan kemudahan perkhidmatan yang disediakan secara percuma oleh TH sepanjang menunaikan ibadah haji. 
Menurut kenyataan itu, demi kebajikan serta keselesaan jemaah haji, pelbagai kemudahan serta perkhidmatan yang disediakan oleh TH di Tanah Suci dan tanah air di tambah baik tanpa sebarang bayaran tambahan seperti perkhidmatan kesihatan, kaunseling, bimbingan dan kewangan. 
“Kerajaan yang sentiasa cakna dalam memartabatkan syiar Islam memberikan sokongan yang berterusan kepada TH melalui kerjasama kukuh dimeterai dengan pelbagai agensi kerajaan lain sejak penubuhannya bagi memudahkan rakyat dalam melaksanakan ibadah haji,” menurut kenyataan itu. 
TH sudah memulakan proses penghantaran surat tawaran menunaikan haji secara berperingkat bermula Isnin lalu. 
Sehubungan itu, bakal haji yang berada dalam penggiliran kuota haji bagi tahun 1439H/2018M dan 1440H/2019M dinasihatkan untuk mengemas kini maklumat peribadi seperti alamat dan nombor telefon masing-masing dengan segera. 
INFO 
* TH tanggung subsidi RM12,470 setiap jemaah musim haji tahun depan 
* TH tanggung subsidi RM9,570 setiap jemaah musim haji lalu 
– BH ONLINE

Co-op services Credit Union Part-Time Teller - Detroit NW in Detroit , Michigan 
Overview 
CO-OP Financial Services is currently looking for a Part Time Teller in our Detroit NW Branch. 
The Teller provides courteous, prompt and accurate service to credit union/members, handles monetary transactions, maintains and processes transaction data, assists in opening and closing duties, and promotes shared branch products, such as, Visa gift cards, and theme park tickets. 
What your day will look like: 
Assists credit union members with monetary transactions, such as deposits, withdrawals, check cashing, loan advance, loan payments, money orders, gift cards, travel cards and other shared branch products purchases. 
Balances cash drawer for transactions handled. 
Assists with micro-encoding/imaging checks, and scanning, vouchers & other items. 
Maintains vouchers and other work materials according to branch procedures. 
Fills voucher counter, brochure racks and lobby pens and keeps a well-maintained lobby. 
Promotes and sells shared branch products. 
Assists in opening and closing duties. 
Qualifications 
To perform this job successfully, the Part-Time Teller must have proficient written and verbal communication skills that demonstrate interpersonal and customer service skills. Must exhibit active listening, professionalism and proper etiquette. Ability to pass computerized teller skills assessment. Experience using computer, keyboard & mouse, calculator and 10-key skills preferred. 
Must exhibit the following service standards: 
Responsible for ensuring that exceptional service is delivered to both internal and external clients by “doing what’s right for credit unions 
Demonstrate enthusiastic support of corporate mission, CO-values and long term objectives. 
Perform job duties within our policies procedures, service standards and state and federal laws. 
We are seeking someone with previous customer service and cash handling experience along with previous sales and cross-selling skills experience. Internal candidates must have had a performance level of 3.0 for the previous review period. High school diploma or G.E.D required; college courses in business preferred. 
Branches are open Monday thru Friday from 9:00 a.m. – 7:00 p.m. and Saturdays from 9:00 a.m. – 2:00 p.m. 
If you or someone you know can perform the duties and responsibilities required of the Part-Time Teller and have the skills and experience required, please submit your resume to be considered for the opportunity. 
About Us 
CO-OP Financial Services is the technology engine that provides access and convenience for credit unions. With over 35 years of credit union service, CO-OP connects credit union members to their accounts through Debit, Credit, ATM, Shared Branching, Member Interaction Services, Mobile, Virtual, and Bill Pay services. CO-OP serves a total of 3,500 member credit unions, 50 million cardholders, 30,000 surcharge-free ATMs, and more than 5,300 shared branches (with 2,000 self-service locations). Handling three billion-plus annual transactions, CO-OP is the nation’s largest credit union service organization—offering resources that enable deeper member engagement to help credit unions prosper.

澳门2017年11月7日电 /美通社/ -- 2017第七届中国（澳门）国际汽车博览会期间，作为展会重要的同期活动之一“未来新物流”--JAC卡车电动化发布会在江淮汽车展台成功举办。安徽省政协党组副书记、副主席张学平，安徽省政协常委、省国资委原主任许崇信、中国机械国际合作股份有限公司党委书记、总经理韩晓军，江淮汽车董事长安进、副总经理佘才荣等受邀参加发布会，海外经销商、媒体、客户共计40余人参加发布会。 
随着国家对新能源政策的支持性增长，新能源汽车无疑成为各大车企发展的重中之重，而JAC将新能源的新技术优势与传统商用车优势相结合，为广大消费者提供 高效化、节能化 的全生态链解决方案。江淮汽车佘才荣副总经理为发布会致欢迎词，介绍了江淮汽车的业务表现和未来规划，JAC国际公司总经理助理余阳通过生动形象的产品定制解决方案发布了新产品JAC电动卡车。根据续航里程的不同需求，JAC将提供纯电动、增程式两套技术方案；针对不同运载量的需求，规划I3、I5、I7三大电动卡车平台，涵盖左右驾、总质量涵盖2.5吨-12吨，每一个平台在同一车架平台上实现不同吨位、不同轴距的柔性拓展。 消息来源: 中国（澳门）国际汽车博览会组委会

posts.text: پیکر مطهر شهید مدافع وطن استوار یکم «حمید رحیم­‌فر» از کارکنان انتظامی استان خراسان شمالی در شیروان و قوچان تشییع و در زادگاهش روستای مزرج به خاک سپرده شد. کد خبر: ۲۶۵۴۰۴   ۱۳:۱۰ - 07November 2017 به گزارش دفاع پرس از خراسان رضوی، مراسم تشییع پیکر مطهر شهید انتظامی استوار یکم «حمید رحیم‌فر» امروز با حضور مردم شهیدپرور، انقلابی و مسئولان استانی و شهرستانی از محل میدان انقلاب شیروان به سمت پارک شهید فهمیده این شهرستان برگزار شد. در ادامه پیکر مطهر این شهید به قوچان انتقال یافت و با حضور اقشار مختلف مردم تشییع و جهت خاکسپاری به زادگاهش روستای مزرج در هشت کیلومتری شهرستان قوچان منتقل شد. گفتنی است، شهید استوار یکم «حمید رحیم‌فر» از کارکنان انتظامی استان خراسان شمالی بود که در 12 آبان 1369 در روستای مزرج شهرستان قوچان چشم به جهان گشود. وی در دوازدهم آبان جهت دستگیری متهم سابقه دار به محل زندگی وی اعزام شده بود که پس از درگیری مسلحانه، شهید رحیم‌فر مجروح شد که در 14 آبان به دلیل شدت جراحات وارده و در حین انتقال به مرکز درمانی مشهد، به مقام رفیع شهادت نائل آمد. از این شهید یک فرزند دختر سه ماهه به یادگار مانده است. انتهای پیام/

posts.title: DIFF 2017: Four-day international film festival concludes with Rima Das’ Village Rockstars
posts.text:
Tweet 
The Dharamshala International Film Festival (DIFF) 2017 came to an end on Sunday. 
The festival, which opened with the acclaimed Mukti Bhawan , wrapped up an impressive line up which included Konkana Sen Sharma’s A Death In The Gunj and Amit V Masurkar’s Newton. The closing film was Rima Das’ Village Rockstars. A still from Village Rockstars. YouTube 
The highlights of the festival were the Indian premiere of Out of this World (USA), a newly restored version of the 1954 film by journalist and writer Lowell Thomas’ fascinating journey to Tibet in 1949. “ I think my father will be very happy. We have talked about it (film) earlier and he knew that we were going to do the project and he was very excited," said Anne Thomas , the daughter of the now deceased filmmaker who presented the film, as reported by The Tibet Post. 
The festival also screened two award-winning documentaries, Machines by Rahul Jain , which has won the World Cinema Documentary Special Jury Award for Excellence in Cinematography at the Sundance Film Festival this year, and Kirsten Johnson’s Cameraperson (USA). 
The festival, in keeping with its focus on experimental and independent cinema, gave a platform to screen feature films such as Ralang Road by Karma Takapa, a film set in Sikkim, which had premiered at this year’s prestigious Karlovy Cary Film Festival; and Puspendra Singh’s Aswathamma, an official selection in the Busan International Film Festival this year. 
Actor-director Konkana Sen Sharma, who presented her directorial debut A Death In The Gunj, spoke at a panel discussion titled 'The State of Independents .' News18 quotes her as saying , "There are films which don’t follow a very typical kind of a formula, and there are also films, which are showing different kinds of peoples but so many Indian films don’t get the funding, the visibility and the eyeballs that they deserve. And that’s because audiences just lap up the same kind of film again and again. So the makers also keep making the same films again and again.” Kalki Koechlin and Vikrant Massey in a still from A Death In The Gunj. YouTube 
She was very enthusiastic about the festival and its venue “It is my first time at Dharamshala and it was magical. I love Tibetan food, the mountains and independent cinema and I am so excited to be here,” she said, as reported by The New Indian Express . Noted actor Adil Hussain also conducted a Masterclass, which saw the actor speak about his process and journey as an actor. 
The festival, which was started by the filmmakers Ritu Sarin and Tenzing SOnam in 2012, has grown to become a film extravaganza nestled in the beautiful Himalayas. The New Indian Express quotes its founder Ritu Sarin as saying, “ The biggest change is the way the festival has grown from being a small local event to a national one. Today, DIFF has become one of the more important venues in India for the new generation of Indian independent filmmakers to come and showcase their film."

グラビアデビューから半年、存在感が増し続けてる小倉。今回は、濡れ髪でいつもより艷やかな姿を披露している。

＊ 話題補給站 諸神的黃昏

＊ 活動報馬仔 好讀玩實驗 

  太空救援站 （圖/取自boredpanda網站） 美國新罕布夏州一個森林裡，最近出現一座廢棄的太空救援站，引起不少人注意。 

雖說這個太空站被「廢棄」，但這其實是90多名10至18歲的學生，在雕刻家、裝置藝術設計師Shing Yin Khor帶領下，設定題目、發想、設計，花了一周的時間建造的作品。 

因為是「太空站」，內部當然會有各種儀表板、太空人的裝備，還有從各個星球收集來的生物標本。而且為了讓剛完成的太空站像被廢棄多時，學生們會用到木工，電線鋪設，噴漆、標本製作、仿舊美化等多種技巧，而這些都是學生過去在露營過程學到的。 

發起這個活動的beam center，是設於紐約的非營利組織，他們的運營宗旨是讓青少年從相互合作、動手做的過程，讓每個人的能力被發現、被拓展。從每年營隊展現的成果來看，參加的學生想必都受益匪淺。 

好讀本周五問：
1.那種暑期活動讓你印象最深刻？
2.你覺得暑期活動的目的應該是？
3.若夏令營要做木工、油漆、牽電線，你會想參加嗎？
4.故事中的夏令營，跟你參加過的活動最不同是？
5.讀完上述的故事後，你的心得？ 

●投稿回答上述五道問題，答案獲選者可得小禮物，編輯部另設有一位特別獎名額，神祕禮相贈。投稿截止時間11月8日周三晚上10：00前，投稿網址由此去： http://educoco.udn.com/photoquest   日本多鬼屋 所有者不明及閒置地 面積等同奧地利 文/陳韻涵 日本福島富岡町的廢棄住宅。在日本，所有者不明及閒置多年的土地與空屋多到快成社會問題。（圖/路透） 新聞故事： 日本人口銳減，各地皆可找到「所有者不明土地」（unclaimed land）或無人居住的「鬼屋」（ghost homes）。日本前總務大臣增田寬也與民間「所有者不明土地問題研究會」共同調查發現，這種情況到了2040年會變得更嚴重，所有者不明及閒置多年的土地與空屋面積將達到8萬3000平方公里，相當於北海道或奧地利的面積。 

美國《大西洋月刊》旗下數位媒體「Quartz」網站引述「所有者不明土地問題研究會」調查報導，日本目前的「所有者不明土地」與空屋面積約4萬1000平方公里，只比九州略大。 

日本目前約有800萬幢空屋，其中許多通常會一直閒置、空盪下去。一旦屋主或地主離世，當局很難追查資產繼承人處理閒置資產，也造成追查稅務的盲點。日本當局在無法確定資產繼承人的部分情況下，繼續將稅款記在死者名下，因為重新登記地契的費用昂貴且程序繁雜。 

日本智庫「東京財團」指出，土地所有權問題阻礙東北地區的重建工作，當地是2011年311東日本大地震引發海嘯的重災區。廢棄空屋可能發生火災，無人處理的垃圾、蔓生的雜草與敗壞的建築結構，都成為公共健康及安全的隱憂。 

就算有些空屋能確認繼承人，也常因缺乏有興趣的買主而難以轉賣。這些屋子大多位於偏遠地區或市郊，難以吸引年輕買家，且日本人不願買二手屋。《金融時報》報導，只有15%的日本人願意買二手屋，但在美國及英國有90%的人願購買。 

為促進買氣和活化土地利用，福井縣等地方政府架設空屋買賣網站，詳列屋況以吸引買主，甚至提供拆屋補貼。日本政府2015年通過一項法案，處罰不主動拆除或翻修空屋的屋主。日本國土交通省上月23日宣布，將允許閒置5年或所有者不明的資產進行「有利的」用途，例如作為農耕地。   諸神的黃昏 文/朱錦華 結合古代神話與科幻的電影近年大行其道。繼《神力女超人》（Wonder Woman）之後，《雷神索爾》也已經拍到到第三集。最新一集《雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏》（Thor:Ragnarok）， 英文片名裡出現一個大家相當陌生的單字：Ragnarok。這個字來自「古北歐語」（Old Norse），意思就是指北歐神話裡諸神與巨人、怪物的最終決戰，中文譯作《諸神的黃昏》。 

《諸神的黃昏》 華格納曠世歌劇 
不過，多數人對《諸神的黃昏》這個詞的認識，來自德國音樂家華格納（Wilhelm Richard Wagner）的作品。華格納晚期的鉅作，當然是四部曲歌劇《尼布龍根的指環》》（Der Ring des Nibelungen），分別為《萊茵的黃金》（Das Rheingold）、《女武神》（Die Walküre）、《齊格菲》（Siegfried），以及壓軸的《諸神的黃昏》（Götterdämmerung）。從1848年開始創作，至1874年完成，歷時共26年。 

《尼布龍根的指環》 啟發《魔戒》 
華格納創作《指環》系列的靈感來自北歐神話以及日爾曼敘事長詩《尼布龍根之歌》（Das Nibelungenlied）。由於有北歐神話的淵源，所以華格納把象徵「萬物同歸於盡、轉換新生」的第四部曲，以Ragnarok的譯意，取名為德語的Götterdämmerung（發音近似「葛塔達馬洪」） 。後來，英語中會用Götterdämmerung一字來形容「一個災難性事件的終結」，例如納粹德國的覆亡。 

《尼布龍根的指環》對後來的西方文創有長久而深遠的影響。我強烈懷疑托爾金（J.R.R. Tolkien）的《魔戒》（The Lord of the Rings），靈感即來自《指環》系列。例如兩者皆以指環代表至高無上的權力來源。「尼布龍根」原意為「尼布龍人」。在《指環》系列裡，「尼布龍人」即指「矮人」（歌劇裡的侏儒），《魔戒》裡則有「哈比人」（Hobbits） 與「咕嚕」（Gollum）。 

《女武神》 因《現代啟示錄》聞名 
《指環》系列可能以第二部《女武神》最為人們熟知。主因之一是名導演柯波拉1979年的越戰電影經典《現代啟示錄》（Apocalypse Now）裡，敘述美軍「第一（空中）騎兵師」（The 1st Cavalry Division）武裝直升機群攻擊越共據點時，就用了《女武神》第三幕的序曲《女武神飛行》（Walkürenritt，英文Ride of the Valkyries）當背景音樂，為成影史上讓人震撼難忘的經典場面。 

此外，二戰時納粹德國曾制訂一個緊急應變計畫（動員後備軍人平亂），代號為「女武神行動」（Unternehmen Walküre）。後來，一群納粹軍官修改了這個計畫，變成刺殺希特勒政變行動勒的一部分，這段歷史多次被搬上銀幕。當中包括湯姆克魯斯主演的《行動代號：華爾奇麗雅》（Valkyrie,2008）。   系列184：「具象」描寫的魔力 文/聯合報寫作教室講師柯惠馨 心中具備「讀者意識」後，必須解決的問題即是：「如何令讀者深刻理解我的想法，經歷我的感受？」循此，鉅細靡遺的告知讀者你的所見所聞、所思所想，則成為重要的意旨。要令讀者能夠「感同身受」的最好方式即是給他許多「細節」，讓他在這些細節中產生「畫面」（這個畫面可能不是作者心中所設定的畫面），並引起屬於自己的共鳴。也就是說，每一個讀者所產生的「共鳴」都可以因其「背景」與「經歷」而形成差異，但也正是此差異，形成文章繽紛的美感。 

「細節」如何產生？如同電影情節般，一針針的「畫面」完成「細節」，一句句「摹寫」完成「畫面」。因此形成文章思路軸線：「摹寫→畫面→細節」。但我們不談基礎「摹寫」，而是透過「摹寫」進階操作，完成畫面，進而達成「文章細節化」的目的。具體細節化可分成三個步驟進行： 

概念具體化 
寫作素材往往自「概念」而發，諸如：美的、醜的、亮彩的……，形容詞紛飛的文句往往阻礙讀者想像力，如果將這些「概念形容詞」使用「摹寫」加工轉化，則易形成有效敘述。如「從後臺簾子�堶悼X來了一個男人，穿了一件藍布長衫，長長的臉兒，一臉疙瘩，雙頰彷彿風乾橘皮似的，皺褶且乾癟，形態甚為醜陋。」透過上述衣著、外型、臉頰等「視覺摹寫」句型，將一個男人的「醜陋」概念化為具體，一覽無遺。 

抽象情緒具體化 
「情緒勃發」是寫作動機，如何將這些動機化成「具象畫面」則成為作者的功力所在。通常我們會使用「摹寫＋修辭」，將抽象情緒烘托呈現。如：「這件事令我記憶深刻，如同身上的疤痕一般，不曾被歲月弭平，每當夜深人靜時，總如鬼魅般映在腦海，常令我魂夢驚坐起。」前述「恐懼」情緒透過「疤痕」、「鬼魅」等「譬喻」修辭，將抽象情緒具體描摹出來，令讀者產生類似「畏怕」的情緒。 

具體事物意象化 
寫作中有些氛圍無法以「單一摹寫」或「簡單譬喻」模擬再現，然可以使用「意象化」進行示現。何謂「意象化」？即是將「具象事物」以「聯想」方式轉化更豐富、更深遠的意趣。並且「聯想內容物」與「原主題」僅部分相似，未有直接關係。如：「秋天的落葉就像沮喪的失業人，垂著頭邁著氣若游絲的步伐，彷彿一個風吹即會隨之墜地，與大地一同腐敗。」以失業人的氛圍形容秋天落葉。然「秋落葉」與「失業人」並無直接關係，僅因類似「沮喪氛圍」而串連，卻令讀者產生畫面感。 

無論用何種「具體化」的技巧，皆是為了將「畫面」完整描繪，有了一個個「畫面」即能拼湊「相關細節」，細節於是在讀者心中發酵，進而產生更豐富的共鳴與內涵，才真正算「作者」與「讀者」之間共感交流。

HUBUNGAN KOS PURATA JANGKA PENDEK (SAC) DENGAN KOS PURATA JANGKA PANJANG (LAC)

Apabila LAC sedang menurun, SAC menyentuh LAC pada bahagian SAC yang juga sedang menurun iaitu di titik A, pada output Q1 di mana SAC1 sedang menurun dengan titik minimumnya di A’.

Apabila LAC di titik minimum, SAC menyentuh LAC pada titik minimum SAC, iaitu di titik B di mana titik minimum SAC0 juga di B pada output Q0.

Apabila LAC sedang meningkat, keluk SAC menyentuh LAC pada bahagian SAC yang juga sedang meningkat iaitu di titik C, pada output Q2 di mana SAC2 sedang meningkat dengan titik minimumnya di C’.

JANGKA MASA PENDEK

Satu tempoh firma tidak dapat menyesuaikan kapasiti lojinya mengikut keperluan pasaran kerana wujudnya faktor tetap dalam operasinya.

Dalam j angka pendek, firma tidak dapat mengeluarkan barang dengan banyak dan hanya dapat menambahkan input berubahnya seperti buruh dengan terhad jika tiada perubahan dalam input tetap contohnya tanah.

Ini bermaksud, tidak kira jika firma itu sudah beroperasi selama 10 tahun atau 2 tahun jika ada faktor tetap dalam operasi, ia sedang berada dalam jangka masa pendek.

Kalau semua faktor adalah faktor berubah, barulah firma beroperasi dalam jangka masa panjang.

JANGKA MASA PANJANG

Satu tempoh firma dapat menyesuaikan kapasiti lojinya mengikut keperluan pasaran kerana semua faktor adalah faktor berubah dalam operasi.

Ini kerana semua faktor dalam operasi adalah faktor berubah.

Firma boleh menaikkan skala pengeluaran, menambahkan modal, meningkatkan tingkat teknologi atau melakukan penyelididkan dan pembangunan untuk menambahkan daya pengeluaran.

Contohnya, firma boleh membuka kilang baru untuk meningkatkan pengeluaran tanah kerana tanah adalah input berubah.

posts.text:
By Patrick Bailey 

If you are having migration issues with the authorities, you better look for a legal representative who will represent you. Not only will the advocate argue your case in court, but also provide the best pieces of advice and help you process documents required. Here are a few tips on identifying the best Washington DC Immigration Lawyers to guide you.

Approach your close associates for help. People you regularly associate with, will always have your best interest at heart. Thus, talk to your relatives, neighbors, workmates, and business associates to help you identify a competent attorney to represent you. In addition, they may play a crucial role in ensuring that you get a good deal when it comes to the bill of costs.

Specialty in immigration matters is fundamental. You should be wary of legal experts who claim to be general practitioners since they may not be up to task. Hence, you should only hire an expert who has specialized in this field of law and had an excellent track record in winning cases. Consequently, the probability of winning the case will be high.

Choose an experienced expert. Practicing for many years, enables an expert fine-tune his legal skills and become the best in the field. Therefore, from the list of recommended experts, pick one who has been practicing for long and has a good record when it comes to service delivery. Moreover, you should confirm the information provided from the relevant authorities.

Draft a budget. The best advocates in the country, charge expensively for their services, which at times may be exorbitant. As a result, get quotations from the various specialists recommended to you and compare to see who offers you some financial reprieve. In addition, if you still consider the rates high, do not feel ashamed to ask for help.

An advocate must be registered. Other than attending law school and graduating highly, a lawyer must be registered with the national bar association and renew his certificate yearly before he can practice. As a result, confirm with your prospective advocate if he has met all the conditions laid for one to observe before practicing.

Work with an advocate of good repute. Nobody wants to be associated with a service provider with a tainted name. Therefore, you should do your part of the homework by ensuring that the expert you are about to hire is not tainted or has previously been accused of mistreating clients. If your potential representative has a dark past, look for other options.

Check the availability of a contract. You cannot trust on word of mouth and therefore, anything you agree upon with your legal representative must be put into writing. Hence, request you expert to draft one, thereafter, read and understand the document. In addition, the document must be well executed to give it legal backing.

Read online articles. The internet has many well-researched articles that can help you make an informed decision. Thus, let your fingers do the walking by typing the right keywords and you will have many materials at your disposal. Furthermore, you will get additional pieces of advice from comments made by fellow readers.

Het Renault Open Innovation Lab in Silicon Valley in Californië heeft een autonoom rijsysteem op punt gesteld dat uitwijkmanoeuvers kan uitvoeren zoals je die aangeleerd krijgt in rijvaardigheidscentra. De constructeur belooft dat de succesgraad van zijn autonoom voertuig, dat Callie is gedoopt, vergelijkbaar is met die van de professionele coureurs die als ijkpunt zijn gebruikt. Het onderzoek wordt uiteraard gebruikt in toekomstige modellen. Renault plant trouwens “meer dan 15 modellen met verschillende graden van autonomie tegen 2022”. posts.author: Adrian Diaconescu
posts.title: Global tablet shipments were down again in Q3 2017, but most top vendors were up
posts.text: Does anyone still care about tablets? Should we even care? Will detachable models like Microsoft’s Surface Pro and Apple’s iPad Pro families be able to save the market from extinction and surpass “traditional” slates in volume despite significantly higher prices? You won’t find answers to far-reaching, long-term questions in the latest International Data Corporation Worldwide Quarterly Tablet Tracker, which looks pretty much the same as the research company’s previous few reports. Once again, global shipments are down year-over-year, this time by 5.4 percent, which actually compares favorably to a huge 14.7 percent annual decline in Q3 2016 numbers , but not so much to the 3.4 percent dip in Q2 sales . Two thirds of the 40 million slates and detachables (convertibles not included) shipped between July and September 2017 came from the world’s top five vendors, leaving a shrinking 33.3 percent slice of the pie for the “others” category and helping consolidate the market at the expense of product variety. Interestingly enough, four of these top five tablet manufacturers reported Q3 growth in both sales and share, while Samsung dipped half a million units, nonetheless retaining its position behind leader Apple. Of course, the gap between iPads and a relatively diverse lineup that however “still relies heavily on the lower cost Tab A and E series” has widened, from a little over six percent back in Q3 2016 to more than ten percentage points now. In third place, Amazon’s ridiculously affordable Fires managed to surge from 3.1 to 4.4 million unit shipments and from 7.5 to 10.9 percent market share, with Huawei and Lenovo practically tied in fourth and fifth as they maintain a “similar strategy of focusing on low-cost devices in Asia/Pacific and Western Europe.” So, no, we have no idea if tablets have a bright future ahead of them (probably not), but right now, the name of the game is value for money. posts.title: Lamborghini Terzo Millennio: zuiver elektrisch
posts.text:
De door Lamborghini en het MIT ontwikkelde hypersportwagen van de toekomst rijdt enkel op elektriciteit. Hij gebruikt supercondensatoren en heeft een zelfherstellend koetswerk. 
Eindelijk onthult Lamborghini de verrassing die het nog maar pas met een teaser aankondigde: de Terzo Millennio. Deze hypersportwagen bundelt heel wat technologie die het merk uit Sant’Agata Bolognese in de toekomst wil gaan gebruiken. Hij is trouwens een waar laboratorium en werd samen met onderzoekers van de Amerikaanse universiteit MIT ontwikkeld. De Terzo Millennio heeft 4 elektromotoren –één per wiel – die worden gevoed met stroom uit supercondensatoren. Die zijn licht en staan garant voor bliksemsnelle acceleraties omdat ze hun energie extreem snel aan de motoren en dus aan de wielen kunnen doorgeven. Zelfherstellend 
Een andere opmerkelijke innovatie van de Terzo Millennio komt van zijn zelfherstellende koetswerk in koolstofvezel. Een vloeistof in microkanalen kan microscopisch kleine scheurtjes dichten. Daarmee blijft de auto krasvrij. En het koetswerk heeft nog een andere opmerkelijke eigenschap: het kan stroom opslaan. Lamborghini wil deze technologie, met onder meer de elektrische aandrijving, in het komende decennium inzetten. De hypercar is bovendien een stijlstudie, want hij is ontworpen door het Centro Stile van de constructeur. We zullen met andere woorden trekken van deze conceptcar terugzien op toekomstige modellen van het merk met het stierenlogo.

وزير النقل يبحث مع شركة أفيك الصينية بدء القطار المكهرب

posts.title: Tesla onthult elektrische vrachtwagen op 16 november
posts.text:
Tesla is niet van plan om de onthulling van zijn elektrische vrachtwagen nog eens uit te stellen: de uitnodigingen voor de presentatie zijn verstuurd. Op 16 november maken we kennis met de stille wegreus. 
Tesla wil niet alleen zijn gamma van personenwagens verder uitbreiden, maar het wil ook het goederenvervoer revolutionariseren met zijn zuiver elektrische vrachtwagen. Zijn oorspronkelijke onthulling was gepland voor september van dit jaar maar werd al vrij vroeg uitgesteld tot oktober. Nu is de voorstelling vastgelegd op 16 november. Die datum lijkt niet meer te kunnen worden gewijzigd, aangezien Tesla een officiële uitnodiging voor het evenement heeft uitgestuurd naar genodigden. Bovendien duiken steeds meer rivalen op. Daimler heeft bijvoorbeeld zijn concept van een elektrische vrachtwagen onthuld tijdens het jongste salon van Tokio. Op de uitnodiging staat een eerste afbeelding van de forse baby bij wijze van voorsmaakje. Voor de technische details is het wel nog even wachten. De productie zou over twee jaar starten.

posts.title: Failing to Initiate Settlement Negotiations is Risky Business
posts.text:
Comments 
Two recent cases have addressed insurance company extracontractual exposure for failing to initiate settlement negotiations. 
In Stalley v. Allstate Insurance Co ., 2016 WL 1752764 (M.D. Fla. April 29, 2016) the court considered the so-called “Powell rule” where the insurance company has an affirmative duty to initiate settlement negotiations under Florida law when the liability of the insured has become clear and the injuries are so serious that a judgment in excess of the policy limits is likely to occur. The Stalley case involved an automobile accident in which Benjamin Hintz was rendered totally incapacitated as a result of a head injury that was received when his scooter was struck by a Volkswagen driven and owned respectively by Emily Boozer and Otto Boozer. The Volkswagen was insured under Emily’s parents’ Allstate policy. The parents’ policy had a $100,000 policy limit. Douglas Stalley brought suit in the status of a third party and guardian of Mr. Hintz. The case went to trial with a jury rendering a verdict in excess of $11 million. Judgment was entered against Emily Boozer in the entire amount of the judgment and against her father, Otto, in the amount of $100,000. 
At the time of the accident, Allstate had several policies available, including two policies which had been issued to Emily Boozer’s grandparents, with one of those policies having a $100,000 liability limit and the other being an umbrella policy with $1 million of liability limits. Allstate ultimately paid $1.1 million under the Boozer parents’ primary policy and under the Boozer grandparents’ umbrella policy in partial satisfaction of the judgment against Emily. Thereafter, Stalley sued Allstate for bad faith. 
Allstate moved for summary judgment, asserting that there was no bad faith in settlement. The federal judge applied Florida’s Powell rule, noting that while Allstate paid one of the policy limits within ten days under the Boozer parents’ policy, the record also reflected that there were two other Allstate policies (apparently unbeknownst to Allstate initially) which were issued to Emily Boozer’s grandparents. Allstate did not offer the $1 million policy limits under the grandparents’ umbrella policy until 1 ½ years after the accident. Under the facts presented, the court found that a fact issue existed to preclude summary judgment regarding whether Allstate should have resolve issues regarding damages and coverage under the grandparents’ policy earlier. 
A similar ruling was reached in Kleinsasser v. Progressive N. Insurance Co., 2016 WL 1583664 (W.D. Okla. April 19, 2016). In the Kleinsasser case, two vehicles struck a cow. The first vehicle to strike the cow was driven by Bellows. The first collision killed the cow. The second vehicle was driven by Michael Kleinsasser. Daniel Caswell was riding in the Kleinsasser vehicle when it struck the cow. Mr. Caswell was injured in the second collision with the cow, which also involved a collision with the rear end of the Bellows pickup truck. 
Progressive Northern settled Mr. Caswell’s claim without notifying Mr. Kleinsasser. No demand had been made by Mr. Caswell. The record reflected that Progressive Northern approached Mr. Caswell to achieve the settlement. Thereafter, Kleinsasser sued Progressive Northern, alleging that it breached the duty of good faith and fair dealing. The Federal District Court noted that Oklahoma law imposed upon insurance companies an affirmative duty to initiate settlement negotiations when an insured’s liability was clear and the injuries of a claimant were so severe that a judgment in excess of the policy limits was likely. Kleinsasser’s complaint pled a bad faith claim based upon Progressive Northern’s settlement with Caswell, in part because Kleinsasser argued that Progressive Northern did not have an obligation to initiate settlement negotiations. The ruling of the district court found that Kleinsasser had sufficiently pled a bad faith claim against Progressive Northern. The district court denied Progressive Northern’s motion for judgment on the pleadings because the face of the bad fad pleadings revealed issues of fact. 
The takeaway from the Stalley and Kleinsasser cases is that bad faith failure to settle cases are very difficult to receive summary judgment on. posts.text: General Electric explores options for aircraft leasing unit -sources * GE considering options following interest from some rivals * GE CEO looking for new divestitures * Asian rivals chipping away at market shares of top lessors * Consolidation intensifies among global aircraft lessors (Adds comment from Flightglobal analyst, sector background) By Anshuman Daga and Greg Roumeliotis SINGAPORE/NEW YORK, Nov 7 (Reuters) - General Electric Co is weighing options for its aircraft leasing operations, including the sale of all or part of the business, as Chief Executive John Flannery searches for new divestitures, according to people familiar with the matter. GE's move on GE Capital Aviation Services (GECAS), the world's second-largest lessor, follows expressions of interest from some of its competitors, the sources said. A spin-off of the business is also a possibility, the sources said, cautioning that GE may decide to keep the business. The move comes at a time when a flood of Chinese funding is shaping the $260 billion-strong aircraft leasing industry as a significant new asset class. GE declined to comment. The sources asked not to be identified because the deliberations are confidential. GECAS has a fleet of roughly 1,300 planes worth an estimated $25 billion, ranking behind only U.S.-listed AerCap Holdings NV , which is estimated to have a $30 billion portfolio, according to data from industry consultancy Ascend Flightglobal. AerCap has a market value of $8.3 billion. Some 40 percent of the airline industry's aircraft is leased to avoid the fixed costs of owning planes. Both GECAS and AerCap trace their roots to the collapsed (Guinness Peat Aviation) (GPA) leasing empire of Irish leasing baron, Tony Ryan, over two decades ago. GE Capital bought $1.3 billion of prime GPA assets and struck a deal to manage most of the rest to form GECAS – coupling GPA's hardware with GE's balance sheet. The remaining core of old GPA was later acquired by AerCap, which is now the main competitor to GECAS. RISE OF ASIAN LESSORS Consolidation in the leasing sector has intensified in the last few years, as Asian competitors chip away at the market shares of GECAS and AerCap. GECAS has also been trimming its fleet in the last few years. "I believe that GECAS sees opportunity in the market to sell aircraft with leases attached to new emerging lessors which allows them to generate profit on these specific transactions whilst also managing their asset and customer concentration risk," said Rob Morris, global head of consultancy at Ascend Flightglobal. Avolon Holdings, owned by China's shipping-and-airline giant HNA Group, has vaulted to become the world's third biggest lessor after acquiring U.S. rival CIT Group Inc's plane leasing business this year. Bank of China-owned Bank of China Aviation Ltd and subsidiaries of Industrial and Commercial Bank of China , China Development Bank and Bank of Communications have emerged among the list of top 15 lessors after placing multi-billion dollar orders for Airbus and Boeing aircraft. In June, GECAS struck a partnership with Caisse de Depot et Placement du Quebec, Canada's second largest pension fund, to create a new company focused on leasing high-tech, fuel-efficient narrow-body aircraft. Flannery has been looking for divestitures to meet his goal of identifying more than $20 billion worth of assets for GE. The company has also been exploring divesting its transportation and healthcare information technology businesses, sources said last month. GE is looking to bounce back after what Flannery said last month were horrible results in the third quarter. He has argued that GE's strong businesses are being held back by others that "drain investment and management resources without the prospect for a substantial reward". Flannery is due to update GE shareholders on the company's strategy at an event on Nov. 13. "Saya lagi di rumah, terus dapat banyak banget message yang nanyain kalau saya bener kerja di Alexis apa enggak. Saya shock banget," kisah Widuri di Mapolda Metro Jaya, Jakarta Selatan (7/11/2017). 
Seperti diketahui, Widuri Agesty telah melaporkan kasus pencatutan tersebut ke SPKT Polda Metro Jaya pagi tadi. Ia melaporkan akun dengan nama Lucil atas tuduhan pencemaran nama baik, penghinaan dan menyebarkan berita bohong. 
"Pasal 310 dan 311 KUHP serta UU ITE Pasal 27 ayat (3) juncto Pasal 45 ayat (1) dan Pasal 28 ayat (1) juncto Pasal 45 a ayat (1). Ancaman pidana penjara enam tahun," terang Krisna Murti selaku kuasa hukum Widuri. 
Dalam kesempatan yang sama, Widuri Agesty juga menceritakan dampak dari pencatutan namanya tersebut. Ia sempat enggan melakukan aktivitas sehari-hari lantaran mendapat perlakuan kurang menyenangkan. 
"Teman yang enggak suka sama saya kan banyak juga. Jadi banyak yang bully," ucap mantan kekasih Jupiter Fortissimo.
